[LAUGHING]

751
01:07:58.825 --> 01:08:03.580
But I just keep on ticking.

752
01:08:04.247 --> 01:08:07.417
Because they promised me that.

753
01:08:07.584 --> 01:08:10.128
- They?
- The dream people.

754
01:08:10.295 --> 01:08:13.506
The ones that gave me this job.

755
01:08:14.257 --> 01:08:16.217
In dreams...

756
01:08:16.384 --> 01:08:20.555
...I am forever.

757
01:08:21.222 --> 01:08:22.724
Too bad you're not.

758
01:08:30.940 --> 01:08:32.275
[WATCH ALARM BEEPING]

759
01:08:33.026 --> 01:08:34.360
[MACHINE BUZZING]

760
01:08:40.867 --> 01:08:42.285
Doc.

761
01:08:42.952 --> 01:08:44.579
Thank God.

762
01:08:46.205 --> 01:08:48.458
I think I've got a way to get him.

763
01:08:49.542 --> 01:08:52.003
TRACY:
So. what's the plan. Doc?

764
01:08:53.838 --> 01:08:55.882
- Thanks.
DOC: You can't get him in a dream.

765
01:08:56.716 --> 01:08:59.844
But if this can come out.
he can come out.

766
01:09:00.011 --> 01:09:02.555
And if he can come out. he can bleed.

767
01:09:02.722 --> 01:09:04.307
- And die.
DOC: Right.

768
01:09:04.474 --> 01:09:06.059
How will you know when I got him?

769
01:09:06.225 --> 01:09:09.062
I'm gonna find you with this
and then I'm bringing you out.

770
01:09:09.228 --> 01:09:11.564
Now. you've got to be holding him
to carry him out.

771
01:09:11.731 --> 01:09:12.774
I know.

772
01:09:12.940 --> 01:09:15.526
Now. he's gonna try and trick you
like he tricked Tracy.

773
01:09:15.693 --> 01:09:19.280
And he's gonna try to use your eyes
to fool you. You'll use these.

774
01:09:19.447 --> 01:09:21.574
- Get the hell out of here.
- You wanna live?

775
01:09:22.408 --> 01:09:24.410
These mean nothing here.

776
01:09:24.577 --> 01:09:27.246
But in the dream.
they can be anything you want.

777
01:09:27.413 --> 01:09:29.707
He got inside of your head.
you get inside of his.

778
01:09:31.167 --> 01:09:32.251
That's my job. isn't it?

779
01:09:32.418 --> 01:09:35.380
Be careful. He's good at finding out
what hurts the most.

780
01:09:35.546 --> 01:09:39.300
DOC: Exactly.
- That's why you gotta take me with you.

781
01:09:39.467 --> 01:09:40.551
I can't.

782
01:09:41.177 --> 01:09:43.763
It's gotta be me and him.

783
01:09:46.808 --> 01:09:48.643
All right. Doc.

784
01:09:49.018 --> 01:09:50.895
Put me in.

785
01:09:55.400 --> 01:09:57.110
Strap her in.

786
01:09:58.277 --> 01:09:59.612
Okay.

787
01:09:59.779 --> 01:10:01.239
Take a deep breath.

788
01:10:01.406 --> 01:10:03.783
- Okay.
- Good.

789
01:10:04.784 --> 01:10:06.285
Ten...

790
01:10:06.911 --> 01:10:07.995
...nine...

791
01:10:08.871 --> 01:10:10.206
...eight...

792
01:10:10.373 --> 01:10:13.251
...seven. six...

793
01:10:13.418 --> 01:10:15.461
...five. four...

794
01:10:16.462 --> 01:10:18.798
...three. two...

795
01:10:20.383 --> 01:10:21.634
...one.

796
01:11:20.193 --> 01:11:22.862
MAGGIE:
And get inside his brain.

797
01:11:35.541 --> 01:11:36.709
[SHOUTING]

798
01:11:55.895 --> 01:11:57.271
[SHOUTING AND LAUGHING]

799
01:13:21.314 --> 01:13:23.733
I'm in his memories.

800
01:13:33.826 --> 01:13:40.583
[CHANTING] <i>Son of a hundred maniacs
Son of a hundred maniacs</i>

801
01:13:40.750 --> 01:13:47.298
<i>Son of a hundred maniacs
Son of a hundred maniacs</i>

802
01:13:47.465 --> 01:13:51.469
<i>Son of a hundred maniacs
Son of a hundred maniacs</i>

803
01:13:55.765 --> 01:13:58.559
Oh. yeah. Ha. ha.

804
01:14:05.191 --> 01:14:07.234
MAN:
Freddy.

805
01:14:09.695 --> 01:14:11.948
Freddy.

806
01:14:14.367 --> 01:14:17.119
You ready for it. boy?

807
01:14:17.703 --> 01:14:21.165
You've been a waste
since the day I took you in.

808
01:14:21.332 --> 01:14:23.918
Now it's time to take your medicine.

809
01:14:27.254 --> 01:14:29.048
[LAUGHING]

810
01:14:30.299 --> 01:14:32.051
Thank you. sir.

811
01:14:33.219 --> 01:14:34.595
May I have another?

812
01:14:34.762 --> 01:14:37.056
[LAUGHING]

813
01:14:40.184 --> 01:14:42.478
You wanna know the secret of pain?

814
01:14:42.645 --> 01:14:46.524
If you just stop feeling it.
you could start using it.

815
01:14:53.197 --> 01:14:57.118
CROWD:
Child murderer! Beast!

816
01:14:57.702 --> 01:14:59.578
Kill him!

817
01:15:11.132 --> 01:15:12.967
Freddy.

818
01:15:14.635 --> 01:15:16.429
We know what you want.

819
01:15:16.595 --> 01:15:19.432
FREDDY: I want it all!
- Of course you do.

820
01:15:19.598 --> 01:15:23.352
- Then open up.
- And you shall be forever.

821
01:15:23.519 --> 01:15:25.271
[FREDDY SCREAMS]

822
01:15:34.030 --> 01:15:35.239
[LORETTA SHOUTING]

823
01:15:35.406 --> 01:15:36.866
[FREDDY GRUNTING]

824
01:15:51.630 --> 01:15:53.716
Mommy.

825
01:15:59.764 --> 01:16:00.890
[CRYING]

826
01:16:03.267 --> 01:16:05.061
Don't worry. baby.

827
01:16:05.227 --> 01:16:09.732
Mommy just had to take her medicine
for snooping in Daddy's special work.

828
01:16:12.443 --> 01:16:15.154
But you won't tell. will you?

829
01:16:15.988 --> 01:16:17.448
I won't tell.

830
01:16:28.793 --> 01:16:32.129
But you did tell. didn't you? Ha. ha.

831
01:16:32.838 --> 01:16:36.592
And now it's time to take your medicine.

832
01:16:37.635 --> 01:16:39.178
[LAUGHING]

833
01:16:42.264 --> 01:16:43.349
You killed my mother!

834
01:16:49.355 --> 01:16:51.273
She's got him.

835
01:16:51.482 --> 01:16:52.817
Let's get her out of there.

836
01:16:54.693 --> 01:16:56.028
[SCREAMING]

837
01:17:07.540 --> 01:17:09.041
[SCREAMING]

838
01:17:15.589 --> 01:17:17.842
I've got you.

839
01:17:18.634 --> 01:17:20.761
I've got you.

840
01:17:24.390 --> 01:17:26.225
I had him.

841
01:17:26.642 --> 01:17:28.853
Where the hell is he?

842
01:17:30.896 --> 01:17:33.399
- Maybe the trip killed him.
- No.

843
01:17:34.233 --> 01:17:36.902
Because I'm still seeing things
the way I did in my dream.

844
01:17:37.069 --> 01:17:38.737
It's not over. Let's go.

845
01:17:48.831 --> 01:17:50.791
DOC: Cops were supposed
to pick this stuff up.

846
01:17:50.958 --> 01:17:54.461
Be glad they didn't. We're gonna have
to hit him with everything we've got.

847
01:17:56.046 --> 01:17:57.631
Whoa!

848
01:17:57.798 --> 01:17:59.633
Check out this knife.

849
01:17:59.800 --> 01:18:01.886
- Hey. put that away.
MAGGIE: That's too small.

850
01:18:08.392 --> 01:18:09.727
Guess so.

851
01:18:09.894 --> 01:18:11.645
DOC:
You sure that's big enough?

852
01:18:12.855 --> 01:18:15.357
- Still believe he's gonna show up. huh?
- Yep.

853
01:18:15.524 --> 01:18:17.193
Come on. Tracy. Over here.

854
01:18:19.403 --> 01:18:21.280
I can feel it.

855
01:18:52.978 --> 01:18:55.981
- You're real here.
FREDDY: It wasn't my fault.

856
01:18:56.649 --> 01:18:58.484
It wasn't.

857
01:18:58.984 --> 01:19:02.238
You saw what they did to me
when I was a kid.

858
01:19:02.404 --> 01:19:03.656
You saw.

859
01:19:05.574 --> 01:19:07.826
I loved you...

860
01:19:08.702 --> 01:19:10.537
...and your mother.

861
01:19:10.704 --> 01:19:13.249
I tried so hard to be good.

862
01:19:14.708 --> 01:19:16.001
I know. Daddy.

863
01:19:17.127 --> 01:19:20.798
But when they took you from me.
it wasn't right.

864
01:19:21.215 --> 01:19:24.134
Oh. I knew you'd believe me.

865
01:19:25.010 --> 01:19:26.136
Come to Daddy.

866
01:19:26.971 --> 01:19:28.514
[SCREAMS]

867
01:19:40.192 --> 01:19:41.235
Maggie.

868
01:19:41.402 --> 01:19:42.611
Over here.

869
01:19:43.654 --> 01:19:45.030
I'm okay.

870
01:19:45.948 --> 01:19:47.700
Maggie. watch out.

871
01:19:53.747 --> 01:19:55.541
- Where's the key?
- I don't know.

872
01:19:57.084 --> 01:19:58.335
The lock's jammed.

873
01:19:58.502 --> 01:20:02.214
I didn't need a glove
to kill your bitch of a mother...

874
01:20:02.381 --> 01:20:06.719
...and I don't need one now.

875
01:20:06.885 --> 01:20:08.012
[GASPING]

876
01:20:14.852 --> 01:20:17.604
Come on. Let go.

877
01:20:20.107 --> 01:20:21.233
Come on. let go.

878
01:20:21.400 --> 01:20:23.610
- No! No!
- No! Get down.

879
01:20:24.695 --> 01:20:26.905
I'll show you how.

880
01:20:33.037 --> 01:20:35.706
Like you showed my mother and Carlos?

881
01:20:37.708 --> 01:20:39.626
And Spencer?

882
01:20:40.669 --> 01:20:43.922
- Give Daddy the glove back. princess.
- Never.

883
01:20:46.175 --> 01:20:47.926
Give it to me.

884
01:20:50.220 --> 01:20:52.097
Give it to me. Give me that glove.

885
01:20:54.099 --> 01:20:55.267
Give me the glove.

886
01:20:55.434 --> 01:20:58.062
In your dreams.

887
01:20:59.271 --> 01:21:00.606
[BOTH SHOUTING AND GRUNTING]

888
01:21:13.869 --> 01:21:15.579
Oh. Daddy.

889
01:21:15.746 --> 01:21:19.666
I remember when we used to hold hands
together when I was a kid.

890
01:21:19.833 --> 01:21:22.127
- I didn't like it then either.
- Aah!

891
01:21:23.337 --> 01:21:26.465
I forgot how much it hurts to be human.

892
01:21:40.562 --> 01:21:42.189
[MAGGIE GROANING
AND FREDDY LAUGHING]

893
01:21:45.818 --> 01:21:47.277
Maggie.

894
01:21:47.444 --> 01:21:49.071
Maggie.

895
01:22:03.419 --> 01:22:04.753
[SHOUTING]

896
01:22:11.468 --> 01:22:12.594
What--?

897
01:22:12.761 --> 01:22:14.012
Come on.

898
01:22:22.312 --> 01:22:23.981
Oh. you--

899
01:22:27.067 --> 01:22:28.527
[FREDDY SCREAMING]

900
01:22:37.119 --> 01:22:38.370
Go ahead.

901
01:22:39.204 --> 01:22:40.622
Put it on.

902
01:22:43.041 --> 01:22:44.418
It's in your blood.

903
01:23:00.934 --> 01:23:03.061
That's it. put it on.

904
01:23:05.481 --> 01:23:07.232
Feels good. doesn't it?

905
01:23:09.359 --> 01:23:11.778
Yeah. Come on.

906
01:23:13.071 --> 01:23:16.158
Let your daddy show you how to use it.

907
01:23:28.170 --> 01:23:29.755
[SCREAMING]

908
01:23:33.091 --> 01:23:35.719
Maggie! Maggie!

909
01:23:42.100 --> 01:23:43.852
Happy Father's Day.

910
01:23:44.019 --> 01:23:45.229
TRACY:
Come on. Doc.

911
01:23:47.439 --> 01:23:49.149
Come on. Yeah.

912
01:23:49.316 --> 01:23:51.777
Come on. let's hurry.
Let's get out of here. Come on.

913
01:23:52.194 --> 01:23:53.779
[GASPS]

914
01:23:54.071 --> 01:23:55.572
Kids.

915
01:23:56.448 --> 01:23:57.616
[SCREAMING]

916
01:24:07.793 --> 01:24:10.337
- You all right?
- Yeah. I'm okay.

917
01:24:14.550 --> 01:24:15.801
[CHUCKLES]

918
01:24:23.809 --> 01:24:25.894
Freddy's dead.

919
01:25:02.889 --> 01:25:04.141
[INAUDIBLE DIALOGUE]
